Thermal Printer
	Direct thermal printer [[img http://www.slxntech.com/images/products/printers/srp350g.gif]]
		Uses heating element to burn dots on heat-sensitive paper
		Commonly used to print receipts
	Thermal Wax printer
		Similar to Dye-sublimination but use film covered with colored wax
